title: Cleveland woman shot with BB gun in the back of the head
text:
Cleveland woman shot with BB gun in the back of the head 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
A 65-year-old woman was shot in the back of the head with a BB gun as she walked home Sunday on Cleveland's West Side....
